80.jpg.webp 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/asXqNm629GQKLdTtrvWFkP-415-80.jpg.webp 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/asXqNm629GQKLdTtrvWFkP-360-80.jpg.webp 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/asXqNm629GQKLdTtrvWFkP-320-80.jpg.webp 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\"/\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/asXqNm629GQKLdTtrvWFkP-320-80.jpg\" alt=\"H\u0026amp;M duvet cover set\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/asXqNm629GQKLdTtrvWFkP-1920-80.jpg 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/asXqNm629GQKLdTtrvWFkP-1600-80.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/asXqNm629GQKLdTtrvWFkP-1280-80.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/asXqNm629GQKLdTtrvWFkP-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/asXqNm629GQKLdTtrvWFkP-768-80.jpg 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/asXqNm629GQKLdTtrvWFkP-415-80.jpg 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/asXqNm629GQKLdTtrvWFkP-360-80.jpg 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/asXqNm629GQKLdTtrvWFkP-320-80.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\" loading=\"lazy\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/asXqNm629GQKLdTtrvWFkP.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/asXqNm629GQKLdTtrvWFkP.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eH\u0026amp;M\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eGingham Duvet Cover Set\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis season, the \u003ca href=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/bedroom/bedroom-decor/gingham-bedding-trend\" data-url=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/bedroom/bedroom-decor/gingham-bedding-trend\" data-hl-processed=\"none\" data-before-rewrite-localise=\"/bedroom/bedroom-decor/gingham-bedding-trend\"\u003egingham bedding trend\u003c/a\u003e is best styled with contrasting patterns for a maximalist look. Add striped sheets in a contrasting colourway for a surprise element when you peel back the covers.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eOne of the reasons H\u0026amp;M\u0026#39;s bedding is such good value is that all of its duvet sets come with two pillowcases included, so you\u0026#39;re not just buying the duvet cover, you\u0026#39;re getting everything you need for a bedding refresh in one fell swoop.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eAnd, as interiors expert Liv Conlon, founder of \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"http://thepropertystagers.co.uk/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" data-url=\"http://thepropertystagers.co.uk/\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\" data-hl-processed=\"none\"\u003eThe Property Stagers\u003c/a\u003e, shares, \u0026#39;upgrading your bedding is one of the simplest ways to make a bedroom look and feel expensive without spending a fortune.\u0026#39;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ePlus, as H\u0026amp;M proves, \u0026#39;you don’t need to splurge on designer brands,\u0026#39; says Liv. \u0026#39;Many budget-friendly retailers offer high-quality options that feel just as indulgent.\u0026#39;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv data-hydrate=\"true\" id=\"slice-container-newsletterForm-articleInbodyContent-fUjHFKNfbdcaDrwUz7gdDG\"\u003e\u003csection\u003e\u003cp\u003eSign up to our newsletter for style and decor inspiration, house makeovers, project advice and more.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://click.linksynergy.com/deeplink?id=kXQk6%2AivFEQ\u0026amp;mid=43250\u0026amp;u1=idealhome-gb-3217301495376203073\u0026amp;murl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hm.com%2Fen_gb%2Fproductpage.1258573001.html\" rel=\"sponsored noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-url=\"https://www2.hm.com/en_gb/productpage.1258573001.html\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\" data-hl-processed=\"hawklinks\" data-placeholder-url=\"https://click.linksynergy.com/deeplink?id=kXQk6%2AivFEQ\u0026amp;mid=43250\u0026amp;u1=hawk-custom-tracking\u0026amp;murl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hm.com%2Fen_gb%2Fproductpage.1258573001.html\" data-google-interstitial=\"false\" data-merchant-name=\"H\u0026amp;M UK\" data-merchant-id=\"226326\" data-merchant-network=\"LS\" data-merchant-url=\"www2.hm.com\"\u003e\u003cfigure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qPzqnDiSNHNjNtJaexbzGQ-1920-80.jpg.webp 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qPzqnDiSNHNjNtJaexbzGQ-1600-80.jpg.webp 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qPzqnDiSNHNjNtJaexbzGQ-1280-80.jpg.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qPzqnDiSNHNjNtJaexbzGQ-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qPzqnDiSNHNjNtJaexbzGQ-768-80.jpg.webp 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qPzqnDiSNHNjNtJaexbzGQ-415-80.jpg.webp 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qPzqnDiSNHNjNtJaexbzGQ-360-80.jpg.webp 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qPzqnDiSNHNjNtJaexbzGQ-320-80.jpg.webp 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\"/\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qPzqnDiSNHNjNtJaexbzGQ-320-80.jpg\" alt=\"H\u0026amp;M duvet cover sets\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qPzqnDiSNHNjNtJaexbzGQ-1920-80.jpg 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qPzqnDiSNHNjNtJaexbzGQ-1600-80.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qPzqnDiSNHNjNtJaexbzGQ-1280-80.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qPzqnDiSNHNjNtJaexbzGQ-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qPzqnDiSNHNjNtJaexbzGQ-768-80.jpg 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qPzqnDiSNHNjNtJaexbzGQ-415-80.jpg 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qPzqnDiSNHNjNtJaexbzGQ-360-80.jpg 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qPzqnDiSNHNjNtJaexbzGQ-320-80.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\" loading=\"lazy\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qPzqnDiSNHNjNtJaexbzGQ.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futur